

                          [help gossip]
-----------------------=========+=========-----------------------
                          
Usage: gossip <message>
 
 This is a public channel. The theme of it is self explanatory and is
 usable for anything but cursing wildly and inappropriate topics. To
 take yourself off of this channel type 'muffle gossip'. To see who
 is on this channel type,'gossip list'. To turn this channel on
 type, 'channel gossip'.                      
 
 For a channel history, type 'gossip history'.
